---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="CERN Research Division"
  description="Weyland-Yutani CERN Research Division. Acquired 2029. Particle physics research, Large Hadron Collider operations, and fundamental science powering applied innovation."
>
  <Header />

  <main class="bg-black pt-36">
    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="relative py-20 border-b-4 border-[#FFC600] overflow-hidden">
      <div class="industrial-grid absolute inset-0 opacity-20"></div>
      <div class="hazard-stripes h-3 absolute top-0 left-0 right-0"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 text-center py-24">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 justify-center mb-8">
          <a href="/research" class="text-[10px] font-mono text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] hover:text-[#FFC600] transition-colors">RESEARCH</a>
          <span class="text-gray-700">/</span>
          <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-[#FFC600] uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">CERN DIVISION</span>
        </div>

        <div class="inline-block px-8 py-3 bg-[#FFC600] text-black font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-8 clip-corner">
          FUNDAMENTAL PHYSICS
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-black text-white mb-8 leading-none uppercase">
          CERN RESEARCH <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">DIVISION</span>
        </h1>

        <div class="h-1 w-64 bg-[#FFC600] mx-auto mb-8"></div>

        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto uppercase tracking-wide font-mono">
          EXPLORING THE FUNDAMENTAL STRUCTURE OF THE UNIVERSE. ACQUIRED 2029. THE FOUNDATION OF EVERYTHING WE BUILD.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="hazard-stripes h-3 absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0"></div>
    </section>

    <!-- STATS -->
    <section class="relative py-14 bg-[#0a0a0a] border-b border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 text-center">
          <div>
            <div class="text-4xl font-black text-[#FFC600]">2029</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-mono uppercase mt-2 tracking-wider">YEAR ACQUIRED</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-4xl font-black text-[#FFC600]">2,400</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-mono uppercase mt-2 tracking-wider">RESEARCH PERSONNEL</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-4xl font-black text-[#FFC600]">27 KM</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-mono uppercase mt-2 tracking-wider">COLLIDER CIRCUMFERENCE</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-4xl font-black text-[#FFC600]">14 TeV</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-mono uppercase mt-2 tracking-wider">COLLISION ENERGY</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- OVERVIEW -->
    <section class="relative py-24 bg-black border-b-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="industrial-grid-dense absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-[10px] font-mono text-[#FFC600] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4">ABOUT THE DIVISION</div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-white mb-6 uppercase">HISTORY AND MISSION</h2>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
            <div>
              <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase leading-relaxed mb-4">
                IN 2029, WEYLAND-YUTANI CORPORATION ACQUIRED THE EUROPEAN ORGANIZATION FOR NUCLEAR RESEARCH, TRANSITIONING IT FROM A PUBLICLY FUNDED INTERGOVERNMENTAL ENTITY TO A DIVISION OF THE CORPORATION'S RESEARCH AND DEVELOPMENT ORGANIZATION. THE ACQUISITION FOLLOWED A PERIOD OF DECLINING GOVERNMENT FUNDING THAT THREATENED THE CONTINUATION OF THE WORLD'S MOST IMPORTANT PARTICLE PHYSICS PROGRAM.
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase leading-relaxed">
                UNDER CORPORATE STEWARDSHIP, CERN HAS RECEIVED UNPRECEDENTED LEVELS OF INVESTMENT. THE LARGE HADRON COLLIDER HAS BEEN UPGRADED TWICE, ACHIEVING COLLISION ENERGIES PREVIOUSLY THOUGHT UNREACHABLE. THE FACILITY'S WORKFORCE HAS GROWN FROM 1,200 TO 2,400 RESEARCHERS.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase leading-relaxed mb-4">
                THE STRATEGIC VALUE OF CERN TO THE CORPORATION CANNOT BE OVERSTATED. FUNDAMENTAL RESEARCH INTO PARTICLE PHYSICS, QUANTUM GRAVITY, AND ANTIMATTER DIRECTLY UNDERLIES THE TECHNOLOGIES THAT DEFINE WEYLAND-YUTANI: FTL PROPULSION, MICRO-FUSION POWER, AND ADVANCED MATERIALS SCIENCE.
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase leading-relaxed">
                THE CORPORATION MAINTAINS CERN'S TRADITION OF OPEN SCIENCE. PUBLICATIONS IN NON-PROPRIETARY RESEARCH AREAS CONTINUE TO BE RELEASED THROUGH PEER-REVIEWED JOURNALS, AND THE FACILITY HOSTS VISITING RESEARCHERS FROM PARTNER INSTITUTIONS WORLDWIDE.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- RESEARCH PROGRAMS -->
    <section class="relative py-24 bg-[#0a0a0a] border-b-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="industrial-grid absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest font-mono">RESEARCH PROGRAMS</span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mt-4 uppercase">
            ACTIVE <span class="text-[#FFC600]">PROGRAMS</span>
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-4 uppercase">QUANTUM GRAVITY</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed mb-4">
              THE CORNERSTONE OF FTL PROPULSION RESEARCH. CERN'S QUANTUM GRAVITY PROGRAM INVESTIGATES THE FUNDAMENTAL RELATIONSHIP BETWEEN GRAVITY AND QUANTUM MECHANICS, PRODUCING THE THEORETICAL FRAMEWORK THAT ENABLES FASTER-THAN-LIGHT TRANSIT.
            </p>
            <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-[#FFC600] tracking-widest bg-[#FFC600]/10 px-3 py-1 clip-corner">CLASSIFICATION: RESTRICTED</span>
          </div>

          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-4 uppercase">ANTIMATTER RESEARCH</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed mb-4">
              THE PRODUCTION, STORAGE, AND APPLICATION OF ANTIMATTER. RESEARCH HAS LED TO ADVANCES IN MICRO-FUSION CELL TECHNOLOGY AND ENERGY STORAGE SYSTEMS DEPLOYED ACROSS ALL CORPORATE PRODUCT LINES.
            </p>
            <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-[#FFC600] tracking-widest bg-[#FFC600]/10 px-3 py-1 clip-corner">CLASSIFICATION: PARTIALLY RESTRICTED</span>
          </div>

          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-4 uppercase">HIGH-ENERGY PHYSICS</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed mb-4">
              COLLIDER EXPERIMENTS PROBING THE STRUCTURE OF MATTER AT THE SMALLEST SCALES. RECENT WORK HAS IDENTIFIED THREE PREVIOUSLY UNKNOWN SUBATOMIC PARTICLES WITH APPLICATIONS IN MATERIALS SCIENCE.
            </p>
            <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-gray-500 tracking-widest bg-[#1a1a1a] px-3 py-1 clip-corner">CLASSIFICATION: OPEN</span>
          </div>

          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-4 uppercase">DARK MATTER DETECTION</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed mb-4">
              ONGOING EXPERIMENTS TO DETECT AND CHARACTERIZE DARK MATTER PARTICLES. THE PROGRAM OPERATES THE WORLD'S MOST SENSITIVE PARTICLE DETECTORS AND COLLABORATES WITH OFF-WORLD OBSERVATION PLATFORMS.
            </p>
            <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-gray-500 tracking-widest bg-[#1a1a1a] px-3 py-1 clip-corner">CLASSIFICATION: OPEN</span>
          </div>

          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-4 uppercase">ADVANCED COMPUTING</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed mb-4">
              THE COMPUTING INFRASTRUCTURE AT CERN PROCESSES MORE DATA THAN ANY OTHER FACILITY ON EARTH. THE DIVISION DEVELOPS NOVEL COMPUTING ARCHITECTURES INCLUDING QUANTUM AND NEUROMORPHIC SYSTEMS.
            </p>
            <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-gray-500 tracking-widest bg-[#1a1a1a] px-3 py-1 clip-corner">CLASSIFICATION: OPEN</span>
          </div>

          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-4 uppercase">THEORETICAL PHYSICS</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed mb-4">
              A DEDICATED THEORETICAL DIVISION WORKS AHEAD OF EXPERIMENTAL CAPABILITIES, PREDICTING PHENOMENA AND PROPOSING NEW AVENUES OF INQUIRY. HOME TO THREE RECIPIENTS OF THE PETER WEYLAND PRIZE IN PHYSICS.
            </p>
            <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-gray-500 tracking-widest bg-[#1a1a1a] px-3 py-1 clip-corner">CLASSIFICATION: OPEN</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FACILITY -->
    <section class="relative py-24 bg-black border-b-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-[10px] font-mono text-[#FFC600] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4">INFRASTRUCTURE</div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-white mb-12 uppercase">FACILITY ASSETS</h2>

          <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
            <div>
              <table class="w-full">
                <thead>
                  <tr class="border-b-2 border-[#FFC600]">
                    <th class="text-left py-3 px-4 text-[10px] font-black text-[#FFC600] uppercase tracking-[0.15em]" colspan="2">LARGE HADRON COLLIDER</th>
                  </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody class="text-xs font-mono uppercase">
                  <tr class="border-b border-[#1a1a1a]">
                    <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-400 w-1/2">CIRCUMFERENCE</td>
                    <td class="py-3 px-4 text-white">27 KILOMETERS</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr class="border-b border-[#1a1a1a]">
                    <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-400">DEPTH</td>
                    <td class="py-3 px-4 text-white">50-175 METERS UNDERGROUND</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr class="border-b border-[#1a1a1a]">
                    <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-400">COLLISION ENERGY</td>
                    <td class="py-3 px-4 text-white">14 TeV (UPGRADED: 28 TeV PLANNED)</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr class="border-b border-[#1a1a1a]">
                    <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-400">SUPERCONDUCTING MAGNETS</td>
                    <td class="py-3 px-4 text-white">9,593</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-400">OPERATING TEMP</td>
                    <td class="py-3 px-4 text-white">1.9K (-271.3C)</td>
                  </tr>
                </tbody>
              </table>
            </div>

            <div>
              <table class="w-full">
                <thead>
                  <tr class="border-b-2 border-[#FFC600]">
                    <th class="text-left py-3 px-4 text-[10px] font-black text-[#FFC600] uppercase tracking-[0.15em]" colspan="2">COMPUTING</th>
                  </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody class="text-xs font-mono uppercase">
                  <tr class="border-b border-[#1a1a1a]">
                    <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-400 w-1/2">DATA CENTER</td>
                    <td class="py-3 px-4 text-white">TIER 1 (1 OF 14 WORLDWIDE)</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr class="border-b border-[#1a1a1a]">
                    <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-400">DATA GENERATED</td>
                    <td class="py-3 px-4 text-white">1+ PETABYTE PER DAY</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr class="border-b border-[#1a1a1a]">
                    <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-400">QUANTUM PROCESSORS</td>
                    <td class="py-3 px-4 text-white">12 (DEDICATED ANALYSIS)</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-400">NETWORK</td>
                    <td class="py-3 px-4 text-white">W-Y SECURE RESEARCH NETWORK</td>
                  </tr>
                </tbody>
              </table>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ACADEMIC PARTNERSHIPS -->
    <section class="relative py-24 bg-[#0a0a0a] border-b-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="industrial-grid absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-[10px] font-mono text-[#FFC600] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4">COLLABORATION</div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-white mb-6 uppercase">ACADEMIC PARTNERSHIPS</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase leading-relaxed mb-12 max-w-3xl">
            CERN MAINTAINS RESEARCH PARTNERSHIPS WITH OVER 80 UNIVERSITIES AND RESEARCH INSTITUTIONS WORLDWIDE. THESE COLLABORATIONS ENSURE THAT THE FACILITY REMAINS AT THE FRONTIER OF FUNDAMENTAL PHYSICS.
          </p>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <div class="corp-card p-8">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-4 uppercase border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-4">VISITING RESEARCHER PROGRAM</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed mb-4">
                CERN HOSTS UP TO 300 VISITING RESEARCHERS ANNUALLY FROM PARTNER INSTITUTIONS. APPOINTMENTS RANGE FROM THREE MONTHS TO TWO YEARS AND INCLUDE FULL ACCESS TO NON-RESTRICTED EXPERIMENTAL FACILITIES AND COMPUTING RESOURCES.
              </p>
              <a href="/research/partnerships" class="text-xs font-bold text-[#FFC600] uppercase tracking-wider hover:text-white transition-colors">LEARN MORE &rarr;</a>
            </div>
            <div class="corp-card p-8">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-4 uppercase border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-4">DOCTORAL PROGRAM</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed mb-4">
                THE CERN DOCTORAL PROGRAM SUPPORTS 60 PHD CANDIDATES AT ANY GIVEN TIME. STUDENTS CONDUCT THESIS RESEARCH USING CERN FACILITIES AND ARE CO-SUPERVISED BY CORPORATE AND UNIVERSITY FACULTY. GRADUATES ARE OFFERED PRIORITY CONSIDERATION FOR CORPORATE RESEARCH POSITIONS.
              </p>
              <a href="/careers/explorers-academy" class="text-xs font-bold text-[#FFC600] uppercase tracking-wider hover:text-white transition-colors">LEARN MORE &rarr;</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- PUBLICATIONS -->
    <section class="relative py-24 bg-black border-b-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-[10px] font-mono text-[#FFC600] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4">OUTPUT</div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-white mb-6 uppercase">PUBLICATIONS AND IMPACT</h2>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
            <div class="corp-card p-8 text-center">
              <div class="text-3xl font-black text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow mb-4">1,200+</div>
              <div class="text-white font-bold text-sm uppercase mb-2">PEER-REVIEWED PUBLICATIONS</div>
              <div class="text-gray-600 font-mono text-xs uppercase">SINCE ACQUISITION</div>
            </div>
            <div class="corp-card p-8 text-center">
              <div class="text-3xl font-black text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow mb-4">47</div>
              <div class="text-white font-bold text-sm uppercase mb-2">PATENTS GRANTED</div>
              <div class="text-gray-600 font-mono text-xs uppercase">APPLIED PHYSICS</div>
            </div>
            <div class="corp-card p-8 text-center">
              <div class="text-3xl font-black text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow mb-4">3</div>
              <div class="text-white font-bold text-sm uppercase mb-2">PETER WEYLAND PRIZE RECIPIENTS</div>
              <div class="text-gray-600 font-mono text-xs uppercase">PHYSICS</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-white mb-4 uppercase border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-4">SELECTED RECENT PUBLICATIONS</h3>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-4">
                <div class="text-xs font-mono text-white uppercase font-bold mb-1">OBSERVATION OF GRAVITON-PHOTON COUPLING AT 28 TeV</div>
                <div class="text-[10px] font-mono text-gray-500 uppercase">CHEN ET AL. PHYSICAL REVIEW LETTERS. 2092.</div>
              </div>
              <div class="border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-4">
                <div class="text-xs font-mono text-white uppercase font-bold mb-1">STABLE ANTIMATTER CONTAINMENT IN MAGNETIC BOTTLE ARRAYS: 10-YEAR RESULTS</div>
                <div class="text-[10px] font-mono text-gray-500 uppercase">NAKAMURA, OSEI, AND BERG. NATURE PHYSICS. 2091.</div>
              </div>
              <div class="border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-4">
                <div class="text-xs font-mono text-white uppercase font-bold mb-1">MEASUREMENT OF THE HIGGS SELF-COUPLING AT NEXT-TO-LEADING ORDER</div>
                <div class="text-[10px] font-mono text-gray-500 uppercase">ATLAS-WEYLAND COLLABORATION. JOURNAL OF HIGH ENERGY PHYSICS. 2091.</div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="text-xs font-mono text-white uppercase font-bold mb-1">QUANTUM VACUUM ENERGY EXTRACTION: THEORETICAL FRAMEWORK AND EXPERIMENTAL LIMITS</div>
                <div class="text-[10px] font-mono text-gray-500 uppercase">RODRIGUEZ AND WEYLAND THEORETICAL PHYSICS GROUP. REVIEWS OF MODERN PHYSICS. 2090.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-6">
              <a href="/research/publications" class="text-xs font-bold text-[#FFC600] uppercase tracking-wider hover:text-white transition-colors">VIEW ALL PUBLICATIONS &rarr;</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="relative py-20 bg-[#0a0a0a]">
      <div class="hazard-stripes h-2 absolute top-0 left-0 right-0"></div>
      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-white mb-6 uppercase">COLLABORATE WITH US</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          FOR ACADEMIC PARTNERSHIP INQUIRIES, VISITING RESEARCHER APPLICATIONS, OR TOUR REQUESTS, CONTACT THE CERN DIVISION ADMINISTRATION.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">CONTACT CERN DIVISION</a>
          <a href="/research" class="btn-secondary">BACK TO RESEARCH</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .clip-corner {
    clip-path: polygon(8px 0, 100% 0, 100% calc(100% - 8px), calc(100% - 8px) 100%, 0 100%, 0 8px);
  }
</style>
